{
  "stem": "20083.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since Gorbandt, who really had a high, a great reputation, he insisted that my father stayed in his ring, and that it somehow helped him, probably even saved his life.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he really-- under his medication or medical supervision, the supervision began to improve.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, when I visited him, there was a huge crowd in front of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't figure out what it was, but I had to worm my way through the mob.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I reached the elevator guy who always-- the lift boy as they called it, the one who always took me to the fifth floor where my father was located.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I asked why there was this crowd.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, you'll see in a minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after about five minutes waiting in the elevator, and I got quite impatient, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I heard people screaming, Heil, Heil, Heil.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought first Hitler would come, but it was actually Goring.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Goring entered the elevator with an SS man and also went to the fifth floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now it just happened to be that this was a very old, creaky elevator and it got stuck between the second and third floor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, the elevator operator got very, very impatient and nervous and because the elevator simply wouldn't budge.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then finally, the SS man got very rough with the driver and elevator operator and they had a little argument.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then Goring said, don't worry, don't worry, everything will be OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It'll just take a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then he became aware of me and we had a little conversation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It only lasted about three or four minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he asked me who I was visiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I told him my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
